# This package SHIPS the derived corpus (data/) so `python reproduce.py` runs offline
# with no LLM and no network. The raw FULL-TEXT corpus is rebuilt locally (README) and
# must never be committed.

# Local config (institutional credentials for the OPTIONAL full-text harvest):
.env

# Rebuilt full-text corpus + harvest working files (copyrighted, local-only):
data/fulltext_pdf/
data/fulltext_md/
data/.pw_profile/

# Python:
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
.venv/

# Regenerated outputs (make reproduce): the three paper figures
fig1_scatter.pdf
fig2_lenses.pdf
fig3_roc.pdf
